# Scheduler & Controller-Manager

## kube-scheduler (notebook 07)

> Watch `Pending` → filter → score → **bind**. Static pod; talks to api-server, never nodes.

## controller-manager — ~30 loops in 1 binary

- **Node** — `NotReady` on heartbeat loss; `NoExecute` taints.
- **Deployment / ReplicaSet** — rollouts; match the count.
- **DaemonSet / StatefulSet / Job / CronJob** — their Pods.
- **Endpoints · ServiceAccount · Namespace · PV-PVC binder · HPA.**

> Bundling is packaging — each loop is independent. **Leader-elected** (lease in `kube-system`): one active in HA.

## cloud-controller-manager

> Split-out cloud bits — Node · Route · **Service (LoadBalancer)**. **Not running on `kind`.**
